information: Crown Organica attaches great importance to the quality of its products and the trust of its customers. Every day we work on expanding our product diversity and developing new products. Our motto is "Food quality starts with the harvest". We always buy high-quality fruits and vegetables in season and process our products carefully. It is very important for us to make the processing and packaging sustainable. Crown Organica produces according to ISO 9001 and ISO 22000 standards and has international certification such as: IFS (International Food Standard), BRC (Bristish Retail Consortium) and Kosher.
